Preamble
This document is a living formal framework. It presents a spine of axioms derived from the intersection of cutting-edge physics, developmental biology, philosophy of mind, and ancient contemplative traditions. Each axiom branches into propositions, and each proposition identifies both its logical consequences and its candidate scientific mechanisms.
The framework is designed to be falsifiable and extensible. Where multiple mechanistic explanations exist, all are listed. Over time, evidence will select between them. The spine remains constant; the filling evolves. An AI system can be trained to track incoming evidence against each mechanism node.
